#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.21:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga "
msgstr "2. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Ānandasutta "
msgstr "21. With Ānanda "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.25, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ … ārāme. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.3"
msgid "“‘nirodho nirodho’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘cessation’. "

#. VAR: nirodho → nirodhā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.4"
msgid "Katamesānaṃ kho, bhante, dhammānaṃ nirodho ‘nirodho’ti vuccatī”ti? "
msgstr "The cessation of what things does this refer to?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.5"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, ānanda, aniccaṃ saṅkhataṃ paṭiccasamuppannaṃ khayadhammaṃ vayadhammaṃ virāgadhammaṃ nirodhadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "“Ānanda, form is impermanent, conditioned, dependently originated, liable to end, vanish, fade away, and cease. "

#. VAR: nirodho → nirodhā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.6"
msgid "Tassa nirodho ‘nirodho’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "Its cessation is what ‘cessation’ refers to. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.7"
msgid "Vedanā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā khayadhammā vayadhammā virāgadhammā nirodhadhammā. "
msgstr "Feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.21:1.8"
msgid "Tassā nirodho ‘nirodho’ti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.9"
msgid "Saññā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.10"
msgid "saṅkhārā aniccā saṅkhatā paṭiccasamuppannā khayadhammā vayadhammā virāgadhammā nirodhadhammā. "
msgstr "Choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.21:1.11"
msgid "Tesaṃ nirodho ‘nirodho’ti vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.12"
msgid "Viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ saṅkhataṃ paṭiccasamuppannaṃ khayadhammaṃ vayadhammaṃ virāgadhammaṃ nirodhadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent, conditioned, dependently originated, liable to end, vanish, fade away, and cease. "

msgctxt "sn22.21:1.13"
msgid "Tassa nirodho ‘nirodho’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "Its cessation is what ‘cessation’ refers to. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.14"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, ānanda, dhammānaṃ nirodho ‘nirodho’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "When they speak of ‘cessation’, its the cessation of these things that this refers to.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.15"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.21:1.16"
msgid "Aniccavaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.21:2.1"
msgid "Aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ anattā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.21:2.2"
msgid "yadaniccāpare tayo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.21:2.3"
msgid "Hetunāpi tayo vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.21:2.4"
msgid "ānandena ca te dasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
